oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: School operated by the Southern Baptist Convention
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of a school operated by the Southern Baptist Convention for grades 8 through 12, located in Butler, Tennessee. Sammy McQueen and Bud Honeycutt are seen on bicycles, and children are sitting on the porch.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Schools; Porches; Bicycles & tricycles
